OL,5, Ofsted's new chief inspector           
OL,6, "understands the extent of change      
OL,7, needed" after the death of head teacher
OL,8, Ruth Perry, her sister has said.       
OL,10,FProf Julia Waters had her first meeting
OL,11,Fwith Sir Martyn Oliver on Thursday, in 
OL,12,Fhis first week in the role.            
OL,14,FShe said she felt reassured that he    
OL,15,Frecognised her calls for "radical" and 
OL,16,F"systemic change" at Ofsted.           
OL,18,FMrs Perry, whose suicide was linked to 
OL,19,Fan inspection by the education         
OL,20,Fwatchdog, died on 8 January 2023.      
